08129 void liftracc_xerbla(int p, const char * rout, const char * form, ...)
08130 {
08131 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 1
08132     liftracc_function_timing_start(&(liftracc_function_profiling_data[LIFTRACC_FUNCTION_XERBLA]));
08133 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ */
08134     va_list argptr;
08135     char *str = 0;
08136 
08137     va_start(argptr, form);
08138     vasprintf(&str, form, argptr);
08139     va_end(argptr);
08140     
08141     void (*liftracc_plugin_func)();
08142     
08143    
08144 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 2
08145     liftracc_function_timing_start(&(liftracc_profiling_data[SELECT_CALL]));
08146 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_  */
08147 
08148 #ifdef _LIFTRACC_SELECTOR_NEW_
08149 
08150     pinfo.info1 = 0;
08151 
08152     *(void **) (&liftracc_plugin_func) = liftracc_selector_select(SELECT_XERBLA, &pinfo);
08153 #else
08154     *(void **) (&liftracc_plugin_func) = liftracc_selector_select("liftracc_plugin_xerbla");
08155 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_SELECTOR_NEW_ */
08156 
08157 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 2
08158     liftracc_function_timing_stop(&(liftracc_profiling_data[SELECT_CALL]));
08159 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_  */
08160 
08161     if (liftracc_plugin_func != 0)  {
08162         // call func without '...'
08163         (*liftracc_plugin_func)(p, rout, str);
08164     } else
08165         ERROR("liftracc_xerbla not executed");
08166 
08167 #if _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ == 1
08168     liftracc_function_timing_stop(&(liftracc_function_profiling_data[LIFTRACC_FUNCTION_XERBLA]));
08169 #endif /* _LIFTRACC_PROFILING_ */
08170 
08171     free(str);
08172 }
